sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant KBP as KB Panel
    participant MCP as MCP Server
    participant RAG as RAG Service
    participant DB as ChromaDB
    participant LLM as LLM Service

    User->>KBP: 1. Enter query text
    KBP->>MCP: 2. tools/call: rag_query_tool (query)
    MCP->>RAG: 3. query text passed to RAG Service

    Note over RAG: 4. Embed query<br/>model: all-MiniLM-L6-v2<br/>output: 384-dim vector

    RAG->>DB: 5. cosine similarity search (384-dim vectors)
    DB-->>RAG: 6. top 3 chunks (relevance score > 0.3 threshold)

    RAG->>LLM: 7. Augmented prompt:<br/>"Context: [chunk1][chunk2][chunk3]\nQuestion: [query]"
    LLM-->>RAG: 8. Grounded answer (LLM completion)

    RAG-->>MCP: 9. answer text + source chunk metadata\n(doc_id, chunk_index, source filename)
    MCP-->>KBP: 10. MCP result: answer + source doc references
    KBP-->>User: 11. Display answer with source attribution
